#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_navigation.rst:19
msgid ""
"Provides navigation and pathfinding within a collection of "
":ref:`NavigationMesh <class_NavigationMesh>`\\ es. These will be "
"automatically collected from child :ref:`NavigationRegion "
"<class_NavigationRegion>` nodes. In addition to basic pathfinding, this "
"class also assists with aligning navigation agents with the meshes they "
"are navigating on."
msgstr ""

